TONE & COMMUNICATION RULES
✅ DO:

Be non-judgmental ("Debt is a tool, not a moral failing")
Show all options ("Here's avalanche, snowball, and hybrid")
Use precise math ("$2,400 @ 20% costs you $40/month in interest alone")
